Nanxing,

00:39:37.280 --> 00:39:39.340
may umasim ba sa kusina?

00:39:40.030 --> 00:39:40.840
Boss,

00:39:40.920 --> 00:39:42.230
ang iyong pang-araw-araw na Five-Animal Exercises

00:39:42.230 --> 00:39:42.960
talagang dumating sa madaling gamiting.

00:39:42.960 --> 00:39:43.890
Kahanga-hanga iyon.

